Nexista is an Open Source PHP/XML/XSL based development framework for building
robust and scalable web applications.

As of 2009, it continues to be in active development after more than five years.
If you are interested in helping with Nexista development, please make a comment
about your intentions at the blog or the forums.

It requires php5-xsl, php-xml, PEAR, MDB2 (for database access), and
MDB2 database drivers.

Current versions can be found at http://www.nexista.org/
